description:
In accordance with Section 4.4 of the Zoning and Development By-law, your request is granted, thereby permitting alterations to your Multiple Dwelling "Multiplex" with a three-storey two-unit front building and a two-storey one-unit rear building with two surface parking spaces having vehicular access from the lane.

M/A to DP-2024-00293:

Building A:
a) Changed the layout of the kitchen;
b) Changed the window size to 1x3646 on the main floor, north elevation;
c) Changed the window size to 1x4050 on the main floor and relocated, east elevation;
d) Changed the window size to 1x3016 on the main floor, west elevation;
e) Removed washer/dryer on the main floor in both units;
f) Changed the den to laundry room on the second floor in both units;
g) Removed interior walls/doors and added attic access doors x4 on the third floor in both units.
Building B:
h) Changed the sizes and locations of the windows to 2x2046 on the main floor, east elevation;
i) Changed the size of the window to 1x6020 OBS on the second floor, south elevation.

As shown on Drawings pages A1.2, A1.3, A1.4, A1.5 and A1.6, submitted by (Qi Li, LQ Design Group Ltd.) "RECEIVED" by this Department on (August 06th, 2025) and now approved as a Minor Amendment to Development Permit Number DP-2024-00293.

Exterior and interior alterations and change of use from existing 2-unit Multiple Conversion Dwelling to Single Detached House on this existing inside with lane site.

Scope of work includes:
New exterior insulation, and new cladding;
New balcony on top of existing entry covered porch;
Removal of existing chimney;
Replacement of windows, removal of 3 window and 2 new windows on east elevation, removal of 1 door on south elevation;
Interior layout change, kitchen & bathroom upgrades, new interior stairs, new finishes;
New heat pump.
